// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
// نبغ (Nabgh) - Educational Platform Database Schema
// ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

generator client {
  provider = "prisma-client-js"
}

datasource db {
  provider          = "postgresql"
  url               = env("DATABASE_URL")
  directUrl         = env("DIRECT_URL")
  relationMode      = "prisma"
}

// ─── Enums ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

enum Role {
  STUDENT
  TEACHER
  PARENT
}

enum Plan {
  FREE
  PREMIUM
  FAMILY
}

enum Difficulty {
  BEGINNER
  INTERMEDIATE
  ADVANCED
}

enum ExerciseType {
  MULTIPLE_CHOICE
  TRUE_FALSE
  FILL_BLANK
}

enum ProgressStatus {
  NOT_STARTED
  IN_PROGRESS
  COMPLETED
}

enum SubscriptionStatus {
  ACTIVE
  CANCELED
  EXPIRED
}

// ─── NextAuth Models ────────────────────────────────────────

model Account {
  id                String  @id @default(cuid())
  userId            String
  type              String
  provider          String
  providerAccountId String
  refresh_token     String?
  access_token      String?
  expires_at        Int?
  token_type        String?
  scope             String?
  id_token          String?
  session_state     String?

  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([provider, providerAccountId])
}

model Session {
  id           String   @id @default(cuid())
  sessionToken String   @unique
  userId       String
  expires      DateTime

  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}

model VerificationToken {
  identifier String
  token      String   @unique
  expires    DateTime

  @@unique([identifier, token])
}

// ─── User ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

model User {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  email         String   @unique
  name          String
  password      String?
  role          Role     @default(STUDENT)
  avatar        String?
  plan          Plan     @default(FREE)
  streak        Int      @default(0)
  xp            Int      @default(0)
  level         Int      @default(1)
  country       String?
  emailVerified DateTime?
  image         String?
  createdAt     DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime @updatedAt

  // NextAuth relations
  accounts    Account[]
  sessions    Session[]

  // Platform relations
  progress          UserProgress[]
  exerciseAnswers   UserExerciseAnswer[]
  flashcards        Flashcard[]
  achievements      UserAchievement[]
  notifications     Notification[]
  subscriptions     Subscription[]
}

// ─── Subject ────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Subject {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  name      String   // Arabic name
  icon      String   // emoji
  color     String   // hex color
  order     Int      // sorting order
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())

  lessons Lesson[]
}

// ─── Lesson ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

model Lesson {
  id          String     @id @default(cuid())
  title       String     // Arabic title
  description String
  content     String     // markdown/HTML content
  subjectId   String
  order       Int        // sorting within subject
  difficulty  Difficulty @default(BEGINNER)
  duration    Int        // estimated minutes
  createdAt   DateTime   @default(now())
  updatedAt   DateTime   @updatedAt

  subject   Subject    @relation(fields: [subjectId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  exercises Exercise[]
  progress  UserProgress[]
}

// ─── Exercise ───────────────────────────────────────────────

model Exercise {
  id            Int          @id @default(autoincrement())
  question      String       // Arabic text
  options       String       // JSON array of options
  correctAnswer Int          // index of correct option
  explanation   String       // Arabic text - why this answer is correct
  lessonId      String
  difficulty    Difficulty   @default(BEGINNER)
  type          ExerciseType @default(MULTIPLE_CHOICE)
  createdAt     DateTime     @default(now())

  lesson   Lesson              @relation(fields: [lessonId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  answers  UserExerciseAnswer[]
}

// ─── UserProgress ───────────────────────────────────────────

model UserProgress {
  id          String        @id @default(cuid())
  userId      String
  lessonId    String
  status      ProgressStatus @default(NOT_STARTED)
  score       Int           @default(0)  // percentage 0-100
  timeSpent   Int           @default(0)  // seconds spent
  completedAt DateTime?

  user  User   @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  lesson Lesson @relation(fields: [lessonId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, lessonId])
}

// ─── UserExerciseAnswer ─────────────────────────────────────

model UserExerciseAnswer {
  id          Int      @id @default(autoincrement())
  userId      String
  exerciseId  Int
  userAnswer  Int      // selected option index
  isCorrect   Boolean
  timeSpent   Int      // seconds
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())

  user     User     @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  exercise Exercise @relation(fields: [exerciseId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}

// ─── Flashcard (Spaced Repetition) ─────────────────────────

model Flashcard {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  front     String   // question side
  back      String   // answer side
  subject   String
  userId    String?  // null = system card, non-null = custom user card
  due       Int      @default(0)    // days until review
  interval  Int      @default(1)    // repetition interval
  ease      Float    @default(2.5)  // ease factor (SM-2)
  reps      Int      @default(0)    // number of successful repetitions
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt

  user User? @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}

// ─── Achievement ────────────────────────────────────────────

model Achievement {
  id           String   @id @default(cuid())
  name         String   // Arabic name
  description  String   // Arabic description
  icon         String   // emoji
  category     String
  requirement  Int      // e.g., "complete 10 lessons"
  createdAt    DateTime @default(now())

  userAchievements UserAchievement[]
}

// ─── UserAchievement ────────────────────────────────────────

model UserAchievement {
  id            String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId        String
  achievementId String
  unlockedAt    DateTime @default(now())

  user        User        @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
  achievement Achievement @relation(fields: [achievementId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)

  @@unique([userId, achievementId])
}

// ─── Notification ───────────────────────────────────────────

model Notification {
  id          String   @id @default(cuid())
  userId      String
  title       String
  description String
  icon        String   // emoji
  read        Boolean  @default(false)
  createdAt   DateTime @default(now())

  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}

// ─── Subscription ───────────────────────────────────────────

model Subscription {
  id            String             @id @default(cuid())
  userId        String
  plan          Plan
  status        SubscriptionStatus @default(ACTIVE)
  startDate     DateTime
  endDate       DateTime
  paymentMethod String?
  createdAt     DateTime           @default(now())
  updatedAt     DateTime           @updatedAt

  user User @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id], onDelete: Cascade)
}
